155
00:07:42,730 --> 00:07:46,160
(Soso Hayama)

156
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,470
The weather is crazy.

157
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,310
It's so nice.

158
00:07:58,340 --> 00:07:59,540
Even the sound.

159
00:08:00,550 --> 00:08:01,850
