161
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:12,460
We always said we should go on a trip abroad.

162
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:16,460
We did come to Japan.

163
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:24,740
Did you get hurt a lot because of me here?

164
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,870
