It was really hard for me when we broke up.

173
00:08:45,860 --> 00:08:46,990
So...

174
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:50,499
I think the bad feelings came out.

175
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:52,460
If you were hurt...

176
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,099
or upset...

177
00:08:55,100 --> 00:08:57,100
