233
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,720
Let's shake hands.

234
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:08,549
(Let's shake hands.)

235
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,620
Get going.

236
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,760
